WEBVTT

00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:02.135
At the end of the appraisal period,

00:00:02.202 --> 00:00:04.871
the Rater conducts an annual appraisal of each Employee's

00:00:04.938 --> 00:00:09.309
performance using his or her performance plan.The Employee

00:00:09.376 --> 00:00:12.779
has an opportunity to supplement the Rater's knowledge about his

00:00:12.846 --> 00:00:16.383
or her performance and related contributions.

00:00:16.449 --> 00:00:19.018
This is accomplished by submitting a self-assessment to

00:00:19.085 --> 00:00:22.922
the Rater within 10 working days after the end of the appraisal

00:00:22.989 --> 00:00:26.960
period. The Rater will consider the self-assessment as he or she

00:00:27.026 --> 00:00:29.829
evaluates the Employee's performance.


